          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y49-111M-line-1" n="1">1<lb/>Here Sarum lies of late so wise</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-111M-line-2" n="2">And learn'd as Tho Aquinas,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-111M-line-3" n="3">He lawn sleeves wore, yet was no more</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-111M-line-4" n="4">A Xtian, than Socinus.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y49-111M-line-5" n="5">2.<lb/>Oaths Pro &amp; Con he swallow'd down,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-111M-line-6" n="6">Lov'd Gold like any Lay-man,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-111M-line-7" n="7">Wrote, preach't, and pray'd, and yet betray'd</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-111M-line-8" n="8">God's holy church for mammon.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y49-111M-line-9" n="9">3.<lb/>Of every Vice he had a spice,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-111M-line-10" n="10">Allthough a Rev<hi rend="superscript">d</hi> Prelate,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-111M-line-11" n="11">Yet liv'd and dy'd, if not bely'd</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-111M-line-12" n="12">A scotch dissenting Zealot.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y49-111M-line-13" n="13">4<lb/>If such a Soul to Heaven has stole,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-111M-line-14" n="14">And scap'd old Satan's Clutches,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-111M-line-15" n="15">We do presume there may be Roome</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-111M-line-16" n="16">For Marl── &amp; his Dutchess.</l>
          </lg>
